               <p>COURT. Q. Are you married? A.There was a ceremony, but in consequence of my first husband being alive, it was put aside - Moore, my first husband, was transported for fourteen years; it was proved he was alive, and I never lived with Mr. Case (my second husband) afterwards - I have not heard of my first husband for four years; I believe he is alive, but am not certain - the fourteen years have been up about a year, but he has not returned; I bought these shoes four months ago.</p>

               <p>Prisoner. Mr. Case came and took away several things, and she called me to turn him out.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18310630-205-person1541">
